headline: BAX Q4 Deep Dive: Mixed Segment Performance and Margin Pressures Shape Outlook
summary: Healthcare company Baxter International (NYSE:BAX) reported Q4 CY2025 results topping the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 8% year on year to $2.97 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.44 per share was 17.8% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
